		<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/b17f4a0a42344cba2f27484e394120e1?s=50&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-50 photo' height='50' width='50' />		<cite class="fn">Sarah</cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>

