		<p>Do you leave the older beans in after adding new ones?  After adding new beans and vodka, do you have to wait another 6-8 weeks?  I don&#8217;t know if I can go that long without baking <img src='http://www.thehungrymouse.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_wink.gif' alt=';)' class='wp-smiley' /> </p>

